FBIS4-37439 "drnes119_r_94005" FBIS-NES-94-119 Daily Report 17 Jun 1994 India Chinese Trade Minister Meets With Officials Chinese Trade Minister Meets With Officials Confers With Steel Minister BK1906072894 Delhi Doordarshan Television Network in English 1630 GMT 17 Jun 94 BK1906072894 Delhi Doordarshan Television Network English BFN [Text] A delegation of the Indo-China Joint Economic Group under the leadership of Chinese Foreign Trade and Economic Cooperation Minister Ms. Wu Yi held a meeting with the minister of state for steel, Mr. Santosh Mohan Dev, in New Delhi today. At the meeting, Ms. Yi said China will support India's entry into the Asia-Pacific Economic Forum. Both the leaders felt that there is tremendous scope for enlarging trade between the two countries.
